HEADWORD: doohickey
<hw>doo"hick*ey</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Any object,
usually a tool or other device, whose name is forgotten, or not
known.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> thingumbob, whatchamacallit, whachamacallit.</syn>
